				<wikidot:authorName>51 47</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4509301</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Been awhile since I read this, but after doing a reread for fun, I feel like a sequel-ish thing could be written from this, taking place a year or so after. The town's so anomalous that they stopped even trying to suppress info about it to townies, kinda like Sloth's Pit. Of course they'd keep things from leaving, but I'd like a day-in-the-life story from an agent's point of view. Maybe I'll get on that, if I can ever stop procrastinating and actually figure out <em>how</em> to save drafts on here.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
