				<wikidot:authorName>Aurabek</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1649410</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I quite like this. The audio version was well done, especially the weather, and the writing was spot on with the tone of the show.</p> <p>Night Vale has always reminded me of the Wiki here, which is I think why I started listening to the show initially. In my head, they've always been connected, somehow or another, but now I have an actual reason. Thanks to you, every time I hear the weather in WTNV, I will know that it wasn't meant to be music. It is just expunged version of what was really meant to be there. Thank goodness for the Foundation intercepting the broadcast.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
